Soil profile
Let‚Äôs now define our soil profile and assign each layer some properties relevant to the driveability study. This is going to be done using the SoilProfile class, which consists of one or more SoilLayers.
Keep in mind the damping and quake parameters are different for the pile base and piel shaft


